posting_body: ['Ask us about our renovations!', 'Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'Come home to a resort-inspired apartment community in Plantation, FL.', 'Our apartments offer an oasis with beautiful lake views and great amenities in studio, one bedroom, two bedroom, and even three bedroom layouts.', 'You will find the perfect selection of modern floor plans with open-concept layouts.', 'Residents love the convenience of a washer and dryer in their apartment home as well as additional storage availability!', 'Amenities:', '-Exterior Storage', '-Frost-free Fridge w/ Icemaker', '-Screen Patio and Balcony', '-Clubhouse', '-Business Center & Resident Lounge', '-Washer/Dryer', '-Industrial-sized Fitness Center', '-Vaulted Ceilings', '-Lake View', '-Two Resort-style Swimming Pools', '-Tennis & Basketball Courts', '-Ceramic Tile Bath', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
